&lt;a rel=&quot;noopener external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;docs.astral.sh&#x2F;uv&#x2F;guides&#x2F;scripts&#x2F;&quot;&gt;single-file scripts&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;, and even
